00:03:12.959 --> 00:03:17.440
The underwater menace of Steven Spielberg's
'Jaws' goes unseen for most of the film. The

00:03:17.440 --> 00:03:22.100
shark finally reveals its incredible size
as Police Chief Brody is throwing chum overboard

00:03:22.100 --> 00:03:27.591
to attract it, leaving him (and the audience)
in shock. As Brody comes to his senses, he

00:03:27.591 --> 00:03:34.150
turns to the vessel's captain to inform him
